Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: bocfx
Version: 0.6.6
Summary: Easy way to get foreign exchange rate from Bank of China.
Home-page: https://github.com/bobleer/bocfx
Author: bobleer
Author-email: liwenbo628@gmail.com
License: UNKNOWN
Description: 
        ## Installation
        
        ```
        ### Required packages
        # pip3 install -U requests scrapy tqdm prettytable numpy matplotlib
        
        pip3 install bocfx
        ```
        
        ## Basic Usage
        ###### As stand-alone	 application
        
        ```
        >> bocfx
        ```
        
        ###### As module
        
        ```
        from bocfx import bocfx
        
        bocfx()
        ```
        
        ## Advanced Usage
        ###### As stand-alone	 application
        
        ```
        bocfx -f -s -t -p -c -o
        ```
        
        ###### As module
        
        ```
        from bocfx import bocfx
        
        bocfx(FX=0, sort=0, time=-1, plot=0, csv=0, pt=0, op='~/bocfx')
        ```
        
